description:
1.  Fuck all you people complaining about the contents.  If you don't like it, fuck off, and go suck the cock of Satan.  I don't care what you think of this compilation.  I just thought it was a good assortment of good music and I would share it to the world in an effort to get these bands name out in the open.  Due to a lot of people blasting me on the title of the torrent I have changed it.  I doubt it will make everyone happy.  Again.  I don't give a shit.


2. I set this torrent up so that you can select the songs you want from it.  Don't give me any shit about how large the file size is.  That is up to you.


3. Last but not least, thank you so much for all you seeders out there.  If it weren't for you, this torrent would have died long ago.  I thank you for your efforts. Cheers

Again.  Fuck all you useless fucks who haven nothing better to do than go troll comments on the piratebay.  Get laid you fucking pricks.

P.S - I know there are a few mislabeled songs in this collection. I am sorry.  Go buy the fucking CD if your unhappy.


Until next time.

-gigsta
